      • buildIssuesJsonList

        public static java.util.List<javax.json.JsonObject> buildIssuesJsonList(java.util.List<IssueResponse> listOfIssueResponses)
        buildIssues constructs a list of Json objects from a list of IssueResponses. This list is used to process the Json objects which represent issues from a repository.
        Parameters:
        listOfIssueResponses - containing the JsonObject list. The JsonObject contains the issues for a repo.
        Returns:
        List of json objects created from all of the JsonObjects in IssueResponse.

      • buildIssuesJsonString

        public static java.lang.String buildIssuesJsonString(java.util.List<javax.json.JsonObject> listOfIssues,
                                                     java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> maxDayRepos,
                                                     java.lang.String topDay)
        buildIssuesJsonString builds the json string for the report.
        Parameters:
        listOfIssues - is the list of issues as JsonObjects
        maxDayRepos - is the Map of repositories that share the top day for issues
        topDay - is the day "YYYY-MM-DD" that had the most issues
        Returns:
        String is the report as a String of Json
